'''Lucrécia Paco''' (yavutse 19 Ukwakira 1969) ni umukinnyi wamafirime muri [[Mozambike]] . Afatwa nk'umwe mu bakinnyi ba filime bazwi cyane muri [[Mozambike]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Paco yakuriye i [[Maputo]] . Akiri umwana, yakundaga kuririmba no kubyina imiziki gakondo, yakandamijwe cyane muri kiriya gihe mbere y’ubwigenge bwa Mozambique mu 1975. Paco yakubiswe ku ishuri azira gukoresha indimi gakondo. Nyuma y'ubwigenge, guverinoma y’abasosiyalisiti yashishikarije amatsinda y’ubuhanzi, kandi yitabira kuririmba, kubyina, no gusoma imivugo. <ref name="gomes">https://web.archive.org/web/20131126221549/http://omenelick2ato.com/entrevistas/lucrecia-paco/</ref>

Mu gihe mu gihe cy'intambara yabenegihugu ya [[Mozambike]], Paco yerekeje ibitekerezo ku ikinamico mu rwego rwa politiki. Yagaragaye muri documentaire ya ''Maputo Mulher'' 1984. <ref>https://clubofmozambique.com/who-is-who-post/lucrecia-paco/</ref> Mu 1986, Paco yari umwe mubashinze itsinda rya Mutumbela Gogo, itsinda ryambere ryamakinamico yabigize umwuga muri Mozambike kugeza na nubu. Yayobowe na firime nyinshi z'Abasoviyeti yarebye, anakora udukino duto twerekana uko kuba Mozambike byari bimeze. Mu rwego rwo gushyigikira itsinda ryamakinamico, Paco nabandi banyamuryango bashinze imigati. <ref name="gomes" />

Paco yafashe ikiruhuko cyimyaka itanu kuri stage kubera umunaniro. <ref name="pila">https://literatasmz.org/post-detail/1</ref> Paco yatumiwe na Instituto Itaú Umuco muri Berezile muri 2009. Yitabiriye umushinga wa Antidote mu mahugurwa mpuzamahanga ku bikorwa by’umuco mu turere tw’amakimbirane, akoresheje ikinamico Mulher Asfalto.  Muri 2010, Paco yakinnye muri film ''Quero Ser uma Estrela'' . Nyuma yaho gato, yakinnye nyamukuru muri ''Nineteens'' , telenovela ya mbere ya Mozambike. <ref name="pila" />

